# TLS certificates go here (generated in Week 3-4)
# See infra/.gitignore — *.pem, *.crt, *.key are excluded from git
#
# Week 3-4 script will generate:
#   ca.pem           — Local CA certificate
#   envoy.crt        — Envoy TLS cert (signed by CA)
#   envoy.key        — Envoy TLS private key
#   service-ca.pem   — mTLS CA for service-to-service
